== Individual items ==
There are also individual items that do not fit into one of the above sets but are of the above item types.

* '''Chests''': Apart from the chests listed in above sets, some chests are only found naturally and are not part of a Furniture set. Most contain unique treasures for their type.
** The {{item|Depth Chest}} is found on [[Glowing Marine Block|special pedestals]] in the [[Aquatic Depths]].
** The {{item|Aquatic Depths Chest}} and {{item|Underworld Chest}} are found in the [[Dungeon]].

